      Creates a Shop object
      Parameters:
      locations - Location of shop sign and chest as Tuple, left = Sign location, right = inventory location
      owner - Owner of the shop as a ShopUser
      shopType - Type of the shop as ShopType
      items - Items to go into the shop as Tuple, left = Product, right = Cost
      players - Users to be added to the shop as Tuple, left = Managers, right = Members
